5956,"position":10,"arabic":"١٤","translation":"(১৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":15,"arabic":"أَفَعَيِينَا بِٱلْخَلْقِ ٱلْأَوَّلِ ۚ بَلْ هُمْ فِى لَبْسٍۢ مِّنْ خَلْقٍۢ جَدِيدٍۢ","translation":"Could We, then, be [thought of as being] worn out by the first creation? Nay - but some people are [still] lost in doubt about [the possibility of] a new creation!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/4645.mp3","surahId":50,"words":[{"id":17145,"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَعَيِينَا","translation":"আমরা তবে অক্ষম হয়ে পড়েছি কি","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17146,"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلْخَلْقِ","translation":"সৃষ্টিতে","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17147,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَوَّلِ ۚ","translation":"প্রথম","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17149,"position":4,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17150,"position":5,"arabic":"هُمْ","translation":"তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17151,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে আছে","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17152,"position":7,"arabic":"لَبْسٍۢ","translation":"সন্দেহের","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17153,"position":8,"arabic":"مِّنْ","translation":"সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17154,"position":9,"arabic":"خَلْقٍۢ","translation":"সৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17155,"position":10,"arabic":"جَدِيدٍۢ","translation":"নতুন","audioUrl":"wbw/050_015_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":17156,"position":11,"arabic":"١٥","translation":"(১৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]}]}